T1  - Status Evolution and Competition: Theory and Evidence
AU  - Washington, Marvin
AU  - Zajac, Edward J.
Y1  - 2005/04/01
PY  - 2005
DA  - 2005/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amj.2005.16928408
